CREATE TABLE `bigquery-public-data.open_images.images`
(
  image_id STRING,
  subset STRING,
  original_url STRING,
  original_landing_url STRING,
  license STRING,
  author_profile_url STRING,
  author STRING,
  title STRING,
  original_size INT64,
  original_md5 STRING,
  thumbnail_300k_url STRING
);

CREATE TABLE `bigquery-public-data.open_images.annotations_bbox`
(
  image_id STRING,
  source STRING,
  label_name STRING,
  confidence FLOAT64,
  x_min FLOAT64,
  x_max FLOAT64,
  y_min FLOAT64,
  y_max FLOAT64,
  is_occluded BOOL,
  is_truncated BOOL,
  is_group_of BOOL,
  is_depiction BOOL,
  is_inside BOOL
);

CREATE TABLE `bigquery-public-data.open_images.labels`
(
  image_id STRING,
  source STRING,
  label_name STRING,
  confidence FLOAT64
);
